### user-service direct (Swagger / service port)
### Swagger UI: http://localhost:8081/swagger-ui/index.html
### OpenAPI: http://localhost:8081/v3/api-docs

@userServiceUrl = http://localhost:8081
@token = REPLACE_WITH_JWT

### OpenAPI document (anonymous allowed on user-service)
GET {{userServiceUrl}}/v3/api-docs
Accept: application/json

### Protected example — list users (JWT)
GET {{userServiceUrl}}/v1/users?page=0&size=5
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Accept: application/json

### Parents API — requires gateway route /api/v1/parents or direct call here (JWT)
# GET {{userServiceUrl}}/v1/parents
# Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
